{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"571fffdb-6b21-4f87-bb7b-22a7af589039","content":"I don't have a skill for **analyzing** crash dumps — the `dump-collect` skill only covers *collecting* them.\n\nHere's how to analyze your `.dmp` file:\n\n### Recommended tools\n\n1. **`dotnet-dump analyze <file.dmp>`** (cross-platform)\n   ```\n   dotnet tool install -g dotnet-dump\n   dotnet-dump analyze crash.dmp\n   ```\n   Useful commands inside the REPL:\n   - `clrstack` — managed call stack\n   - `pe` — print last exception\n   - `dumpheap -stat` — heap summary\n   - `threads` — list all threads\n\n2. **WinDbg** (Windows) with SOS extension — richest experience\n\n3. **`lldb` + SOS** (Linux/macOS)\n\n### Quick triage steps\n\n1. Run `pe` (print exception) to see if there's an unhandled exception\n2. Run `clrstack` to see where the crash occurred\n3. Run `threads` then switch to each thread (`setthread <id>`) and run `clrstack` to find the faulting thread\n\nWould you like me to install `dotnet-dump` and walk through the analysis if you can provide the dump file path?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f8372b55-9ce5-4867-ae8a-1c5ab47aed61","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a .dmp crash dump file from a .NET app and wants help analyzing it. Let me check if there's a relevant skill for this. Looking at the available skills:\n\n- `dump-collect` - This is for *collecting* crash dumps, not analyzing them. The description explicitly says \"DO NOT USE FOR: analyzing or debugging dumps, post-mortem investigation with lldb/windbg/dotnet-dump analyze\"\n- `android-tombstone-symbolication` - For Android tombstones, not .dmp files\n- `apple-crash-symbolication` - For Apple .ips crash logs\n\nNone of the available skills are for analyzing .dmp files. \n\nSince I don't have a specialized skill for this, I'll walk through the general approaches for analyzing .NET crash dumps.","outputTokens":473,"requestId":"DA05:30132C:6CA8302:7572884:6A03DA17"},"id":"578c7f04-d4c9-4e93-b40d-9ae7cc986b4a","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:55:48.103Z","parentId":"bd7465d3-12a6-44a8-b7f8-7e95de4a52dd"}
